{"tid":1077526,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"希特拉 & 中國副總理：一個國家、一種文化、一種語言","createTime":"2019-03-25T15:40:46.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-26T00:47:24.000Z","uid":47714,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"892c0ffa81fb059e853f917248b86f9632d8020c","tid":1077526,"uid":47714,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-25T15:40:46.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=cm94JlIzvJg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3Dcm94JlIzvJg&d=Fb7z1ilWoLc7MobAJ3fbq%2FLVWyXx0XMfrvcdwhNvS5Y%3D&h=4971c6d7\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=cm94JlIzvJg</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Q8XZ14R.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FQ8XZ14R.png&h=8cd48d5e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n一個國家、一種文化、一種語言<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://news.tvb.com/programmes/newsfile/5c89ab1ee60383e42c3d2754\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.tvb.com%2Fprogrammes%2Fnewsfile%2F5c89ab1ee60383e42c3d2754&d=Fb7z1ilWoLc7MobAJ3fbq%2FLVWyXx0XMfrvcdwhNvS5Y%3D&h=5f3d48dd\" target=\"_blank\">http://news.tvb.com/programmes/newsfile/5c89ab1ee60383e42c3d2754</a><br />\n<br />\n1998年3月，副總理兼外長錢其琛向港區人大代表講述「一國兩制」中「一國」的概念，重溫當年的報道。<br />\n<br />\n長期主管香港事務的副總理兼外長錢其琛，早上成為第一位出席香港區人大代表會議的中央官員。他和專責溝通內地及香港事務的港澳辦公室主任廖暉，一起聽取委員的意見。<br />\n<br />\n會議採用閉門形式進行，記者只是有五分鐘的時間拍攝，之後全部都要離開。<br />\n<br />\n港區人大團長吳康民會後引述錢其琛在會上，提到「一國兩制」中「一國」的概念。"},{"pid":"52b5e7e3eb45cb97f7f8fd808dcd392d42ae554c","tid":1077526,"uid":149496,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-25T15:44:32.000Z","msg":"希特拉?"},{"pid":"9556580b242539adccfbf24a2af6e3e09047e233","tid":1077526,"uid":47714,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"52b5e7e3eb45cb97f7f8fd808dcd392d42ae554c","tid":1077526,"uid":149496,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-25T15:44:32.000Z","msg":"希特拉?"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-25T15:56:17.000